# Security

- Clerk handles auth — verify JWT in NestJS guard, never roll custom auth.
- Never commit secrets — use .env.local, document in .env.example only.
- Validate all user input via DTOs before processing.
- Scope all database queries to authenticated userId.
- Webhook endpoints verify Svix signatures (Clerk webhooks).
- CORS restricted to known app origins.
- File uploads: validate mime type and size; store outside web root.
